FORM CORR_MAINT_/SPROLIMS/VCCARA USING VALUE(CM_ACTION) RC.
  DATA: RETCODE LIKE SY-SUBRC, COUNT TYPE I, TRSP_KEYLEN TYPE SYFLENG.
  FIELD-SYMBOLS: <TAB_KEY_X> TYPE X.
  CLEAR RC.
MOVE /SPROLIMS/VCCARA-OTKAT TO
/SPROLIMS/TCCARA-OTKAT .
MOVE /SPROLIMS/VCCARA-WERKS TO
/SPROLIMS/TCCARA-WERKS .
MOVE /SPROLIMS/VCCARA-CLASS TO
/SPROLIMS/TCCARA-CLASS .
MOVE /SPROLIMS/VCCARA-MANDT TO
/SPROLIMS/TCCARA-MANDT .
  CORR_KEYTAB             =  E071K.
  CORR_KEYTAB-OBJNAME     = '/SPROLIMS/TCCARA'.
  IF NOT <vim_corr_keyx> IS ASSIGNED.
    ASSIGN CORR_KEYTAB-TABKEY TO <vim_corr_keyx> CASTING.
  ENDIF.
  ASSIGN /SPROLIMS/TCCARA TO <TAB_KEY_X> CASTING.
  PERFORM VIM_GET_TRSPKEYLEN
    USING '/SPROLIMS/TCCARA'
    CHANGING TRSP_KEYLEN.
  <VIM_CORR_KEYX>(TRSP_KEYLEN) = <TAB_KEY_X>(TRSP_KEYLEN).
  PERFORM UPDATE_CORR_KEYTAB USING CM_ACTION RETCODE.
  ADD: RETCODE TO RC, 1 TO COUNT.
  IF RC LT COUNT AND CM_ACTION NE PRUEFEN.
    CLEAR RC.
  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.
